<H2>Current Research</H2>
<MENU>
<!WA7><A HREF="http://now.cs.berkeley.edu/">Berkeley NOW</A>: Software and hardware support for using a network of workstations as a distributed supercomputer.
<P>
<!WA8><A HREF="http://now.cs.berkeley.edu/Glunix/glunix.html">GLUnix (Global Layer UNIX)</A>: a virtual operating system layer for a NOW
<P>
<!WA9><A HREF="http://now.cs.berkeley.edu/Xfs/xfs.html">xFS</A>: serverless network file service
</MENU><br>

